# OKF bundle slot — baked into the air-gap image at /kb.
#
# Stage your knowledge bundle here (one OKF concept per markdown file) BEFORE
# running deploy/build-image.sh, e.g.:
#
#   cp -r kb/* deploy/kb-data/
#
# Leaving this slot empty produces a valid image with an empty /kb; populate it
# at runtime by mounting a bundle or running `pixkb ingest` instead.
